		<title>狗狗對人的態度大不同？這「五個原因」是改變關鍵！ </title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/09/27/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e5%b0%8d%e4%ba%ba%e7%9a%84%e6%85%8b%e5%ba%a6%e5%a4%a7%e4%b8%8d%e5%90%8c%ef%bc%9f%e9%80%99%e3%80%8c%e4%ba%94%e5%80%8b%e5%8e%9f%e5%9b%a0%e3%80%8d%e6%98%af%e6%94%b9%e8%ae%8a%e9%97%9c/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 洪瑜蓉]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sat, 27 Sep 2025 06:02:58 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
